Dialogue: 5,0:01:08.61,0:01:09.90,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's May.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:11.79,0:01:14.81,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is bright and green.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:22.17,0:01:31.19,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I considered myself the closest to you out of all of the guys.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:31.19,0:01:33.23,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not necessarily true.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:40.89,0:01:44.37,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,What did he mean by that?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:45.92,0:01:50.07,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,How should I have responded to that?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:50.71,0:01:52.76,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't stop thinking about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:53.63,0:01:57.48,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kazehaya only said that to me out of kindness,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:57.48,0:02:01.75,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,but I overreacted and responded to him with...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:06.66,0:02:08.45,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,That was so rude of me!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:09.20,0:02:12.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Man, he's so thick. He didn't even wait for you!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:12.26,0:02:14.89,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously. Maybe it's all in my head.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:14.89,0:02:18.82,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It must be because of how he compliments you!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.10,0:02:33.59,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I really am... creepy.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:44.01,0:02:50.35,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to have a natural relationship \N with Kazehaya...  Like before.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.81,0:02:57.57,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,But now I don't remember what that was like.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.40,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.40,0:03:02.60,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doing anything during lunch break today?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.60,0:03:04.91,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,It's so nice out I thought I'd go play soccer.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.78,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you my bicycle kick!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.01,0:03:09.68,Alt,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya and his buddies are going out to play soccer again?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.68,0:03:11.51,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Nakai, Negishi. Why don't you guys play with us?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:11.51,0:03:12.20,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.20,0:03:12.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You sure?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.50,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are on the soccer team!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.50,0:03:15.72,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you guys are really good.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.40,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Teach us how to head the ball!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.40,0:03:19.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, of course!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:19.17,0:03:20.01,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:25.53,0:03:27.22,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.78,0:03:31.53,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, be nice and friendly, natural...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.53,0:03:34.16,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morning.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.14,0:03:46.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.47,0:03:48.12,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.94,0:03:57.13,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya treated me the same way he treats everyone...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.57,0:04:01.47,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. I guess that's why he's known as Mr. Lively.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.67,0:04:08.16,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard not to stare after being \N greeted with such a beaming smile.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.79,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sadako.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.26,0:04:21.38,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's being so nice and friendly and normal this morning too!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.37,0:04:25.46,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good mo—
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.46,0:04:27.07,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,No good, no good. You look so tense.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.86,0:04:30.29,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Morning~
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.67,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Mor~ning~?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.67,0:04:34.25,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Your forehead!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.61,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35}MORNING!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.61,0:04:37.73,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,No, more like this.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.73,0:04:38.95,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Morninggg!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.95,0:04:39.80,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, your turn.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.80,0:04:40.86,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,MoRn—
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.44,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Morninggg!!!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.22,0:04:42.52,Alt,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,They're at it again.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.44,0:04:43.65,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Morning~~~
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.11,0:04:44.34,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,He just doesn't quit.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.65,0:04:44.33,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Morning~!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.70,0:04:45.88,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40}MORNING!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.88,0:04:47.25,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Mooorning!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.25,0:04:48.59,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}MorninG!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.84,0:04:50.03,Alt,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,What a pair.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:55.57,0:04:56.93,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:58.03,0:05:01.40,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we think of it as kindness,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.31,0:05:09.07,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,that "kindness" means something completely different to Kazehaya than it does to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.07,0:05:13.37,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, my stomach hurts...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.87,0:05:16.93,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I've been kind of constipated lately...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.54,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That sucks.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.15,0:05:23.92,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.92,0:05:25.47,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd Sawako go?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.47,0:05:26.79,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the bathroom?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.99,0:05:32.12,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,This is good for constipation...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.12,0:05:33.15,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That plant?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:33.15,0:05:35.14,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do with that?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.14,0:05:38.90,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,There she goes again.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:41.16,0:05:42.20,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Shota?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.15,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.44,0:05:53.76,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.71,0:05:56.58,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,You've been kinda down lately.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.00,0:05:59.19,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Have I?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.19,0:06:00.08,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.06,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, next!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.88,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a new class now.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.16,0:06:12.76,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe it was normal to say something like that to help her get used to the new class.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.29,0:06:17.77,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,But I made her even more uncomfortable instead.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:18.88,0:06:19.81,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.34,0:06:21.33,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:22.01,0:06:23.31,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,"Something like that"...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.41,0:06:25.38,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly did you—
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.62,0:06:25.78,Alt,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna talk about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.20,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,So selfish.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.70,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:30.70,0:06:35.66,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Deep down, I'm pretty selfish, \N possessive, and like things my way.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.66,0:06:37.00,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,And quick tempered.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.72,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm just about out of patience.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.72,0:06:44.74,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I know it'll be difficult for her, but I really want to stop beating around the bush.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:45.83,0:06:46.77,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:47.86,0:06:49.45,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,is your idea of patience?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.45,0:06:53.53,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not like I want to make things difficult for her.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.14,0:07:01.78,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried so hard to get this far.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.90,0:07:06.93,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,But doesn't she like you too?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.33,0:07:12.18,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she doesn't dislike me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:16.91,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(181,91)}He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:16.91,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(975,139)}He got\N(courtesy)\Nchocolate
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.98,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya is just so lively!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.39,0:07:21.86,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I admire him so much!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.39,0:07:24.17,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,And respect him!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.50,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,But that's it!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.36,0:07:35.15,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What part of me is lively? Jeez!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.84,0:07:38.23,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,No one said that.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.38,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in some sort of rush?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.66,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.21,0:07:51.38,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else might have their eyes on her too.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.13,0:07:57.36,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,When I think of someone else being with her...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.97,0:08:01.83,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,It bothers me.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:03.48,0:08:05.74,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Is she really that attractive?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.38,0:08:10.01,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like a traditional Japanese doll to me...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.26,0:08:14.15,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but hang in there.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.15,0:08:16.19,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't very comforting.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:21.72,0:08:23.89,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako, where are you going?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.52,0:08:31.54,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind coming with me?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.88,0:08:37.59,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to my medicinal plant corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.70,Garden,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(112,375)}Detox
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.70,Garden,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(1038,370)}Insomnia
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.69,0:08:42.03,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What are these signs for?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.03,0:08:45.21,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might be helpful to let everyone know what they do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:45.87,Garden,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)\frz354.246\move(542,357,1096,702,0,10617)}Detox
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:55.84,Garden,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs20\3c&HF3F6F7&\frz358.996\move(183,25,735,370,0,10617)}Constipation\NDiarrhea
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.87,0:08:49.09,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see. Don't you normally write the name of the plant?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:55.84,Garden,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz354.246\move(739,480,1093,702,0,6867)}Detox
Dialogue: 5,0:08:49.09,0:08:52.11,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be easier to understand if I wrote what they're used for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:53.84,Garden,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)\fs25\move(-38,167,128,270,0,3195)}Hair Loss
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.11,0:08:55.84,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,It seems more like these plants will cause what's written!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.16,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.16,0:08:59.92,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Plants and signs from "The Curse"!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.75,0:09:03.98,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,What if I wrote "affects" or "for" on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:07.15,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\frz4.934\pos(626,567)}Diuresis
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:07.15,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz3.794\pos(627,536)}For
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.80,0:09:06.43,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,That's so small.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.43,0:09:08.35,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,"For diuresis"?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.26,0:09:14.47,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Kent!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:14.47,0:09:17.39,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you all called me by first name!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.39,0:09:19.07,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.08,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya suddenly came to mind.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.56,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.29,Alt,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,You were hoping someone would visit you, right, Sadako?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.75,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Someone you like?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.82,0:09:34.01,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a psychic.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.85,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,A p-psychic!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.47,0:09:39.90,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Not only does he act natural,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:39.90,0:09:41.45,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,not only is he friendly,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.39,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,but he's a psychic too!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.39,0:09:45.82,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Your face looks strained!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:46.87,0:09:50.93,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that girls shouldn't make faces like that!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:50.93,0:09:56.55,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a philanthropist, so when a girl looks like she's abandoning everything that makes girls happy,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.28,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't ignore her.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.94,0:10:02.08,Italics,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who does he think he is?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.79,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Abandoning?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.79,0:10:06.35,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.17,0:10:12.00,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! When I do this, you smile!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.20,0:10:16.34,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that? Did I really just see that?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.34,0:10:21.20,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,And she has such a great role model like you to look up to, right, Ayane?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.20,0:10:23.47,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. Now get out of my face.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:23.47,0:10:26.65,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Yoshida, have a fine pair of legs.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.15,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Sadako?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.32,0:10:42.83,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it looks like she's straining her face.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.83,0:10:46.11,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you stop forcing her to smile?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.11,0:10:47.29,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:51.63,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs70\bord0\c&HA0816C&\fnCreativeBlock BB\frz346.352\pos(1042,366)\b0}Strained
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:51.63,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs70\bord0\fnCreativeBlock BB\frz1.498\c&H7A3682&\pos(199,301)}Scary
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.90,0:10:56.07,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I... I... want to become friendly, Teacher!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.07,0:10:57.20,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.08,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.08,0:11:00.90,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,That has a nice ring to it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:00.90,0:11:03.43,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best, Psychic Teacher!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.43,0:11:04.39,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Your forehead again!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.10,0:11:07.95,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up the psychic and teacher parts.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.00,0:11:10.31,Italics,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What does this guy want?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.76,0:11:13.85,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Kent!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.85,0:11:15.61,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.61,0:11:17.97,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How's your new class?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.97,0:11:19.66,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any cute girls?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.66,0:11:23.77,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'd call her cute, but there's someone who interests me.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.77,0:11:25.89,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Tell us about her!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.89,0:11:27.21,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,She's dark and super tense!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.21,0:11:28.50,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.01,0:11:33.57,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What's your deal?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.31,0:11:36.89,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Ayane.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.89,0:11:38.63,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.89,0:11:40.26,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Planning?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.33,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Me? What makes you think that?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.33,0:11:45.94,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are making a lot of passes at Sawako.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.93,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,But doesn't Sawako like Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:53.03,0:11:54.10,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,So she does.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.10,0:11:57.87,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't do something uncalled-for, got it?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.87,0:11:59.72,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,This is a really crucial time for her.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:00.16,0:12:01.96,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Crucial time?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:03.98,0:12:07.23,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'm a good guy.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.33,0:12:10.13,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.26,0:12:16.23,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really "okay"?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.46,0:12:31.14,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,This will be on the midterm!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.66,0:12:34.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Man, midterms already?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.34,0:12:35.88,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.88,0:12:40.94,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Sadako's cursed notes were passed around freshman year in class D!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.47,0:12:45.86,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't cursed. Our class average was really high thanks to those notes.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.86,0:12:47.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What, seriously?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.59,0:12:48.58,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, seriously!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.58,0:12:49.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:49.30,0:12:53.77,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,On the midterm, Sadako's cursed notes \N cursed you into getting a high score!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:53.77,0:12:55.67,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, that's not it—
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.67,0:12:58.30,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Boys! This will be on the midterm!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.14,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.14,0:13:05.77,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako's notes really helped us on last year's midterm.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.77,0:13:08.81,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're really good at academics!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:08.81,0:13:10.01,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Good?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.01,0:13:12.43,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,This is kind of important...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.75,0:13:18.46,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Hey guys, Sadako said that she'd hold a crash course for the midterm after school today!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.71,0:13:25.99,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,C-Crash course?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.37,0:13:30.89,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going to do something that crazy?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:33.23,0:13:35.67,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,You'll do it, right, Sadako?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.67,0:13:37.29,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the middle of class at the moment...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.46,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind me doing it...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.35,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I can even tell around three ghost stories now!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.15,0:13:48.66,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can live up to their expectations?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.66,0:13:51.18,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone's expecting you to tell ghost stories.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.90,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, four people came!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.90,0:13:59.09,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako, you...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:59.09,0:14:01.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really need this crash course!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:01.26,0:14:02.07,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.07,0:14:05.69,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Kent ain't coming even though he announced it?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.61,0:14:12.99,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Have you guys started already?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.99,0:14:15.78,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,We're just about to.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.93,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh good. I just made it!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.29,0:14:25.69,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya came too.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.35,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.35,0:14:30.17,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,We just finished cleaning.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.17,0:14:31.87,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sadako!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.13,0:14:37.84,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, thank you!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.72,0:14:39.95,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,You're really doing it?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:39.95,0:14:41.23,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:41.23,0:14:43.88,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Kazehaya about it earlier.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.69,0:14:49.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ryu?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.08,0:14:50.10,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Baseball practice.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.10,0:14:51.95,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya told her...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.61,0:14:55.16,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sadako?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.31,0:15:00.03,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I can help,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.03,0:15:01.67,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.37,0:15:05.65,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's a pretty big group.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.65,0:15:09.31,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Kazehaya was telling people about it earlier.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.31,0:15:10.80,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Lively?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.16,0:15:14.94,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They say he can't ignore people who need help fitting in.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.57,0:15:17.98,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.47,0:15:21.98,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,You'll come too, right, Tsuru?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.69,0:15:27.81,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,First, for this section, what you need to do is remember the formula.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.81,0:15:29.94,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? I can't see!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:29.94,0:15:33.46,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako, use the blackboard.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:34.01,0:15:35.40,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,B-Black—
Dialogue: 5,0:15:35.40,0:15:36.25,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Great idea!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.25,0:15:37.92,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,That'll make taking notes much easier.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.70,0:15:41.45,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You heard them. Get going!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.88,0:15:43.62,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.66,0:16:25.34,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,I-I got it!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.34,0:16:26.17,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.17,0:16:28.13,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,2 root 5!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.17,0:16:31.05,Default,Class,0000,0000,0000,,The dunce duo got it!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.34,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's easy to get now!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:33.34,0:16:34.88,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Sadako!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.45,0:16:40.38,Italics,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,It's time, Sadako!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.86,0:16:57.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen her smile before!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.07,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Even Sadako smiles!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:00.55,0:17:03.19,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,When Sadako smiles, it means good fortune is on the way!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:03.19,0:17:05.13,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it before!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.13,0:17:07.93,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it countless times before!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.93,0:17:09.42,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,This is a competition?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.13,0:17:13.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that was great.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.35,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And we understand the problems now too.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.35,0:17:17.94,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad we came to this review!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.48,0:17:44.91,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sadako!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.91,0:17:46.83,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Teach us again, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.83,0:17:47.90,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.25,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks for coming!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:50.77,0:17:52.13,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.96,0:17:54.61,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.85,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,You worked really hard to do \N something outside of your comfort zone.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.85,0:17:59.34,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Teacher!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:04.24,0:18:05.58,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.58,0:18:07.78,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't impossible. Definitely ain't.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.05,0:18:11.08,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Ant?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.65,0:18:21.32,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Think you can go without me?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:23.58,0:18:27.18,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I have something important to take care of.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.16,0:18:31.00,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:33.01,0:18:34.00,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:35.58,0:18:37.63,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako, we're in a bit of a hurry.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.49,0:18:43.33,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted to do a safety inspection, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:44.17,0:18:45.82,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:45.82,0:18:47.97,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna take off, Sawako.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.06,0:19:10.30,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I'll thank him more naturally and like a friend.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.38,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.33,0:19:16.92,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I interrupted him!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.73,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. You go first.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.41,0:19:21.26,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.89,0:19:30.41,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I just... wanted to say thank you for today.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:32.56,0:19:36.86,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be able to thank him better, but I just can't do it.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:37.71,0:19:39.61,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he made me so happy...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:43.00,0:19:48.75,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think standing up there in \N front of people is my thing, but I—
Dialogue: 5,0:19:48.75,0:19:49.72,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:50.79,0:19:51.60,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.16,0:19:56.71,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I think you have a knack for teaching.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.88,0:20:09.57,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I never, ever want Kazehaya to hate me.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:20.76,0:20:23.49,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and about what I said that day...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.68,0:20:29.45,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.56,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:02.49,0:21:03.43,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.85,0:21:11.94,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for you.
